Trevor Morgan (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Trevor_Morgan_(actor) 0 Trevor John Morgan (born November 26, 1986) is an American actor. He has appeared in the films Genius, The Sixth Sense, The Patriot, A Rumor of Angels, Jurassic Park III, The Glass House, Chasing 3000, Mean Creek, Barney's Great Adventure based on the popular children’s television series, Local Color, Family Plan, and Uncle Nino.
